Amid all the morbid facts, there are many who provide inspiration to the others to not give up. An elderly man, who lives in Paldi was shocked when he was diagnosed as HIV positive in 1998. Today, he has turned his life around and has become an inspiration for others living with the disease. “Initially, I broke down completely when I came to know that I was diagnosed with HIV. My business too collapsed owing to this. But later I decided to fight back and I learned to live with the disease. I am now helping others to live a full life even with AIDS,” he said. 

